deprecation.message: Support for Xamarin applications will end on May 1st, 2024 (for more info, see https://dotnet.microsoft.com/platform/support/policy/xamarin). As such, support for the Intune MAM SDK Xamarin bindings will also end on the same date. Please migrate your app to .Net/MAUI and use the new Intune .Net/MAUI bindings instead.

description: Enables mobile app management features with Microsoft Intune for iOS apps built with Xamarin.
licenseUrl: https://github.com/msintuneappsdk/intune-app-sdk-xamarin/blob/master/Microsoft License Terms Intune App SDK Xamarin Component.pdf
releaseNotes: Contains version 15.3.0 of the Microsoft Intune App SDK for iOS and version 1.1.26 of the Microsoft Authentication Library (MSAL) for iOS. Building for simulators on Apple Silicon is not supported yet.
title: Microsoft Intune App SDK for Xamarin.iOS
